id: pm-2p7a
title: "TypeScript-only extension loading: ship .ts entry, load via Node native type stripping (no compiled .js)"
description: "Implement ADR pm-m1uz: convert the extension/package loading model from 'TS source compiled to a committed index.js the loader imports' to 'TS source IS the manifest entry (./index.ts), loaded directly via Node >=22.18 native type stripping — no compiled .js, no build step'. Scope: bump engines to >=22.18 and @types/node to ^22; point every manifest entry (first-party packages, docs/examples, scaffolder output) at ./index.ts; delete committed compiled .js; update runtime-loaders + gen-package-runtime-loaders.mjs to resolve runtime.ts (drop the JS loader variant); retarget CI (ci/nightly/auto-release/docs workflows) and the esbuild bundler to Node 22/24 (drop Node 20); add tsconfig.examples.json + allowImportingTsExtensions; fix the scaffolder next_steps (no 'npm run build') and README/docstring drift; reconcile all test fixtures (runtime.js->runtime.ts, manifest entry, scaffold package.json scripts) and the dogfood/smoke harnesses (no compile, load .ts directly)."
type: Feature
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[6]: "area:extensions","area:sdk",authoring,breaking-change,ci,loader
created_at: "2026-06-24T07:24:07.989Z"
updated_at: "2026-06-24T10:37:41.548Z"
author: claude-code-agent
parent: pm-ugqx
resolution: "TypeScript-only extension/package loading delivered and PR #353 follow-up failures fixed: .ts source is the manifest entry loaded by Node native type stripping, package runtime loaders rethrow missing dependencies inside discovered runtime.ts, scaffolded packages declare engines.node >=22.18.0, tsconfig examples allow explicit .ts imports, CI now has a Node 22 TypeScript package-runtime smoke, and stale scaffolder metadata/changelog state is reconciled through pm."
expected_result: "All extension/package loading is TypeScript-only with 100% coverage, green dogfood/smoke gates, and a working manual smoke; docs/docstrings reframed; auto-release healthy."
actual_result: "Verified after PR #353 current-head review follow-up: dependency-free Node 22 runtime-loader smoke passes locally under mise node@22.21.1; pm-beads/pm-todos package runtimes load SDK values from PM_CLI_PACKAGE_ROOT/dist/sdk/index.js, preserve dynamic SDK import failures as Error.cause, validate required EXIT_CODE members before accepting SDK modules, and match missing-runtime ERR_MODULE_NOT_FOUND messages using native, file URL, and forward-slashed normalized paths for Windows robustness; package-first dogfood passes 88 commands; manual temp smoke passes with zero doctor/health warnings; full coverage passes 248 files / 5001 tests at exact 100% statements/branches/functions/lines; typecheck, static quality, contracts, security scan, audit, Sentry/telemetry gate, external package smoke, docs/skills, and release gates are green."
